### 9. Script de build pour la documentation

**`scripts/build_docs.sh`** :
```bash
#!/bin/bash

echo "🔨 Building unified documentation..."

# Build Rust docs
echo "📚 Building Rust documentation..."
cargo doc --workspace --no-deps

# Build Python docs (si applicable)
echo "🐍 Building Python documentation..."
cd python_lib
python -m pdoc --html --output-dir ../docs/api/python ftp_core_python

cd ..

# Build MkDocs site
echo "🌐 Building MkDocs site..."
cd docs
mkdocs build

echo "✅ Documentation built successfully!"
```